ensions. We present results on randomized worlds with up to 1024 agents and\ncompare success rates against state-of-the-art MAPF planners. Finally, we\nexperimentally validate the learned policies in a hybrid simulation of a\nfactory mockup, involving both real-world and simulated robots.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2018 18:18:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 18:20:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2019 23:56:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-02"}
