 to identify cut distance limits using spectra of\ngraphons. We also show that continuous cut distance identifying graphon\nparameters have the {\\guillemotleft}pumping property{\\guillemotright}, and thus\ncan be used in the proof of the Frieze-Kannan regularity lemma.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 11:36:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2018 09:56:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 May 2019 11:49:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 14:13:18 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 2 Sep 2021 12:30:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-19"}
