e when the supershell was not already\nsupersonically expanding; it was a result of the density increase due to the\ngalactic shear and oscillations perpendicular to the disc of the Milky Way.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 13:27:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
